BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:-7rKbe6NR27ASelJ9HjWB
SUMMARY:Service Sunday
DTSTAMP:20260307T235944Z
DTSTART:20260308T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:This is the Sunday where we join in work projects around our co
	mmunity as we BE the church! There are multiple service project locations 
	around Magnolia with projects ranging from making blankets for kids enteri
	ng foster care to habitat restoration! Afterwards\\\, we will all meet in 
	MUCC’s Pilgrim Hall for cocoa and soup. Some locations have limited spots 
	so register here today! \\nHere is the list of this year’s Projects: \\n\\
	nProject Linus: Upstairs in Pilgrim Hall we will have a team that will mak
	e fleece blankets for kids going into Foster Care.  No sewing experience r
	equired!  This project is great for folks of all ages.\\nMagnolia Park Hab
	itat Restoration: The team will work under the direction of Seattle Green 
	to remove aggressive weeds and maintain areas where weeds have been remove
	d.  All equipment provided.\\nDiscovery Park Habitat Restoration: The team
	 at Discovery Park will be doing outdoor habitat restoration.  All equipme
	nt provided.\\nSeattle Animal Shelter: The team at SAS will be doing proje
	cts in service of sheltered animals (Children must be 12+ and have adult s
	upervision).\\nBookmarks for Inmates for Hagar’s Ministry: The team will m
	aking bookmarks at MUCC in the Parlor for women at the Washington Correcti
	ons Center for Women.\\nBallard Food Bank Hygiene Repack Prep: The team (w
	orking at Magnolia Presbyterian) will help to repack bulk Hygiene\\\, Pet\
	\\, and Dry Foods into smaller packages so that the Food Bank can keep its
	 shelves stocked with these much needed items.\\nDaybreak Star Cultural Ce
	nter: Working at the Daybreak Star Cultural Center at Discovery Park\\\, p
	articipants at this site will be involved in outdoor gardening\\\, restora
	tion and help with landscaping projects around the Center and in their Eld
	er Garden.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/service-sunday/\n\nFrom D
	iscover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/service-sunday/
LOCATION:Magnolia United Church of Christ\\\, 3555 W McGraw St\\\, Seattle\
	\\, WA\\\, 98199\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
CATEGORIES:Discover Magnolia
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
