BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kjBSpEoN4h-G-Sa3HxaWs
SUMMARY:Glass Class: Book Cover Coasters
DTSTAMP:20260307T235945Z
DTSTART:20260411T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Cozy-up with a mug of tea and your favorite book… but oh no! Wh
	ere are all the coasters? Have no fear! We’ve got just the solution to pro
	tect your precious objects from destructive heat and moisture — glass book
	 coasters. That’s right! Coasters designed by you to look just like your f
	avorite book cover or classic novels\\\, so that you can enjoy your next b
	ook with some extra special\\\, on-theme decor. \\nIn this 3-hour glass ch
	arm workshop\\\, you will build unique compositions using Elmer’s glue and
	 a variety of glass dots\\\, stringers\\\, shapes\\\, and more. Learn the 
	fundamentals of fusing while experimenting with a new medium and exploring
	 the many possibilities! Cost includes all tools and supplies as well as m
	aterials for up to 2 coasters per person. Finished pieces will be ready fo
	r pick-up at the workshop location after 1 week.\n\nhttps://myballard.com/
	event/glass-class-book-cover-coasters/\n\nFrom My Ballard
URL:https://myballard.com/event/glass-class-book-cover-coasters/
LOCATION:Swoon City\\\, 1716 NW Market St\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98107\\\, 
	United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:myballard
CATEGORIES:My Ballard
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
